21
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,630
What?

22
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:44,420
When you suggested creating a webtoon,

23
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:46,040
I should've said no, no matter what.

24
00:01:46,040 --> 00:01:48,470
