148
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:57,850
You didn't spill coffee on him.

149
00:11:57,850 --> 00:11:59,310
Think positively.

150
00:11:59,310 --> 00:12:02,750
Hold on. I appreciate you comforting me,

151
00:12:02,750 --> 00:12:05,160
